<p>I am currently employed as a technical consultant by <a title="OpenText Corporate Site" href="http://www.opentext.com" target="_blank">OpenText</a>, a provider of enterprise content management solutions. My historic background is as a web content management technical solution architect, originally employed by Obtree, a company subsequently acquired by Ixos. My current position at OpenText is as a result of the acquisition of Ixos in 2006.</p>
