INSERT [content_version] ([id], [content_id], [version_id], [state_id], [data], [edit_user], [updated_date]) VALUES (54, 3, 5, 1, '<h2>CCMS</h2>
<p>CCMS, or &#39;Clare&#39;s Content Management System&#39;, is a CMS I have been writing. Originally written in Perl and file-system based I have now ported it to classic ASP, with server-side javascript as the scripting language with versioned content and database support.&nbsp;</p>
<p>This site is using the ASP version of CCMS, and is fully manageable - pages, content and navigations are all under the control of the author. They are of course constrained by the underlying site design and code managing the automatic creation of navigations based on the page hierarchy.</p>
<p>I am currently in the early stages of porting CCMS to .NET using C#.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, '26/08/2010 17:53:57')
